      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INTREPIDUS (3) has a strong overall record having 10 wins and 10 places from 30 starts but was out of the money last time when fourth (25.77) over 450m at Shepparton. Solid record at the distance winning nine races. Has the ability and looks a key chance this line-up. ASTON BUGSY (7) had been racing in honest fashion recording three placings in a row before finishing fourth (31.13) at The Meadows latest. The form out of last race has been strong. Key runner on best form. HERE COMES BILLY (2) is a talented type with an excellent strike rate at this journey. Has been on speed to score at his last couple of runs. Scored latest at Traralgon in a handy 24.01. Can continue on with his winning form. PARUMBA JAZZMAN (1) is not to be discarded.",
